('aed2d256-e4c6-578f-a995-fdc3bee99395', '84743bae-a8da-408e-9c48-c37bcb27e7c4', 'Because the school is getting bigger, the number of students will ___ next year.', '因為學校正在擴大，明年學生人數將會增加。', 'increase', 'decrease', 'forget', 'remain', 'in- (進入/向內) + crease (增加/生長) → 增加。', 'in (進入) + crease (增加) → 進入增加的狀態 → 增加。', '2026-07-08 09:07:21', '2026-07-08 09:07:21'),
